        java.lang.String getOpenTags()

      • setOpenTags

        void setOpenTags​(java.lang.String openTags)
        Sets the list of EMV tags for Fast track operation, that must be returned to ECR in raw TLV view without encryption.
        Parameters:
        openTags - The string formatted by next pattern: Every tag must be coded by 4 byte on text hex view. For the example, tag DF82 looks like as 0000DF82 and tag 82 looks like 00000082. Multiple tags writes as 0000DF8200000082. This string may be begun from 0x prefix. Case type may be any.

      • getEncTags

      • setEncTags

        void setEncTags​(java.lang.String encTags)
        Sets the list of EMV tags for Fast track operation, that must be returned to ECR in encrypted TLV view.
        Parameters:
        encTags - The string formatted by next pattern: Every tag must be coded by 4 byte on text hex view. For the example, tag DF82 looks like as 0000DF82 and tag 82 looks like 00000082. Multiple tags writes as 0000DF8200000082. This string may be begun from 0x prefix. Case type may be any.
